<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="shake-off">shake off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>摆脱；甩掉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The evening walk was a time to shake off the day’s upsets.  
傍晚时分的散步是摆脱一天的心烦意乱的时候。</p><footer>2015 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You can’t shake off the sun with one hand.
只手难遮天。</p></div></div>